01:28:08,989 --> 01:28:09,824
- Mr. Justin.

1478
01:28:11,158 --> 01:28:12,091
- Hi, Wishbone.

1479
01:28:12,093 --> 01:28:13,658
I hope you are okay.

1480
01:28:13,660 --> 01:28:14,993
I'm fine.

