01:32:14,735 --> 01:32:16,337
- They bought one of my scripts.

1556
01:32:17,404 --> 01:32:18,305
- Oh my God.

1557
01:32:19,306 --> 01:32:20,138
For real?

1558
01:32:20,140 --> 01:32:21,373
- Yeah, for real.

